crates/mdbook-compare/README.md
     1â†’# mdbook-compare
     3â†’This is a simple utility to compare the output of two different versions of mdbook.
     4â†’
     5â†’To use this:
     6â†’
     7â†’1. Install [`tidy`](https://www.html-tidy.org/).
     8â†’2. Install or build the initial version of mdbook that you want to compare.
     9â†’3. Install or build the new version of mdbook that you want to compare.
    10â†’4. Run `mdbook-compare` with the arguments to the mdbook executables and the books to build.
    11â†’
