     1â†’# mdbook-core
     7â†’This is the base support library for [mdBook](https://rust-lang.github.io/mdBook/). It is intended for internal use only. Other mdBook crates depend on this for any types that are shared across the crates.
     8â†’
     9â†’> This crate is maintained by the mdBook team, primarily for use by mdBook and not intended for external use (except as a transitive dependency). This crate may make major changes to its APIs or be deprecated without warning.
    10â†’

