crates/mdbook-driver/README.md
     1â†’# mdbook-driver
     7â†’This is the high-level Rust library for running [mdBook](https://rust-lang.github.io/mdBook/). New books can be created using [`BookBuilder`](https://docs.rs/mdbook-driver/latest/mdbook_driver/init/struct.BookBuilder.html). The primary type [`MDBook`](https://docs.rs/mdbook-driver/latest/mdbook_driver/struct.MDBook.html) can be used to manage and render books.
     8â†’
     9â†’> This crate is maintained by the mdBook team for use by the wider ecosystem. This crate follows [semver compatibility](https://doc.rust-lang.org/cargo/reference/semver.html) for its APIs.
    10â†’

